== Trolling ==

A group called the "Al-Aqsa Trolling Crew" had already been contributing to [[Chasethehedgehog]] and [[DestinyMew]] related [[drama]] on dA.  In September, after a raid on a [[forum]] site called "Grim Azubastion", they discovered Daniel and his dA account.  He really [[asking for it|brought it on himself]], considering the fact that he commented on one of the [[User:Anon1Guardian|troll's]] [[YouTube]] pages telling him how he was going to [[Lulz in hell trollfags|go to hell]] for the raid.  After reading his writings and journals of [[Incontinent Student Bodies|bawww]], they knew [[trolling|what had to be done]].

