==== Cool Story, Bro ====

At some point, the [[trolls]] convinced one of the forum members to [[win|join their side]].  Daniel was [[butthurt|outraged]] and even went to the point of ''writing a story '' about it.  This story is [[lulzy]] in the fact that it portrayed the trolls as evil murderers and Daniel as a [[bullshit|helpless victim]], rather than the sick [[pedophile]] he is.  The original story can be read [http://legi0n.789chan.org/pwn/src/story.txt here], but one [[retard|internet wizard]] also took the liberty of creating a dramatic narration.

