=== Daniel's thought on being [[owned|trolled]] ===

The following was posted [http://azusanity.wikia.com/wiki/User:Daniel_Benfield here].

On September 27, 2009 Daniel ran into some trouble with trolls. The chief blow-away moment was when [[Fag|Oppdis]] announced that he was renouncing [[Azumanga Daioh|Azu]] (although later developments showed that he was in fact always a troll...just not Azu until 9/27/09). After a troublesome battle that involved &ndash;
* A YouTube [[troll|user]] named WarloBarker88 (given name "Daniel Benfeld") spreading lies about Daniel
* [[lulzy|Nasty]] edits to the second-generation AzuSanity Wiki
* A DeviantART user posting pictures [[Copyright|stealing]] both the original and Great Battle "Azu-WHO" logos (plus several others, all mocking Daniel)
* A [[chatroom]] [[trolling|ambush/backstabbing/beatdown]] on October 1
* Repeated abuse of [[Mary Sue|Hannah Benfield]] throughout (essentially claiming that she was both a [[transsexual]] and giving "BJs")

...Daniel, for his own safety, posted a goodbye on DeviantART on October 2, 2009. With this, he changed his signature to the last line spoken by the Fourth [[pedophile|Doctor]] ("It's the end, but the moment has been prepared for.") and posted a goodbye that ended with the First Doctor's famous speech to his granddaughter [[Whore|Susan]] ("One day, I shall come back...")

On October 8, 2009, following a formal complaint to the DeviantART [[Nazis|Help Desk]] by Daniel, [[troll|Anon1Guardian]] was [[permab&|banned permanently]] from the site. [[Oh noes|Since then, Daniel expressed an interest in returning to DeviantART]].

[[Shit no one cares about|On October 13, Daniel returned to DeviantART with a new oneshot entitled "Mind's Vortex". In addition, he changed his signature.]]

=== Son, I am Disappoint ===
{{quote|Hey, folks...this is going to be hard for me, [[no|and perhaps even you]].|Daniel, assuming anyone gives a fuck}}
On the 21st and 22nd of Febuary 2010 respectively, Daniel posted a [[BAWWW|pair of blogs]] in which he whined about his dad, [[the man|Phillip Benfield Sr]]. In his first blog, Benfield goes on about how he found his bony old father [[LOL|lying on the floor after hitting his head on a dresser]]. As a result of this [[lulzy|unfortunate]] accident, Daniel's father was put on life support. Poor Phillip couldn't even get a liver transplant due to his having been a drunken [[poor|bum]] for [[over 9000|so many]] years. Further showing what a [[unwarrented self-importance|selfish and self-centered]] prick he is, Daniel goes on further to state that he ''[[asshole|refused to see his own father in the hospital]]''.
{{quote|I refused to go to the hospital, as I did not wish to see my father with even more tubes sticking out of him.|Daniel not giving a shit}}

In his second bawwwlog, Daniel updates [[noone|all zero people who give a shit]] on his father's health by stating that Phillip has [[dead|kicked the bucket]]. Instead of hoping for the best for Phillip [[otherkin|in the next life]], Daniel (in true [[christfag]] style) decides to be dick to his dead father by implying that Phillip could very well have gone to [[hell]]. Probably because daddy [[drunk|was hitting the sauce]] a little to often.

